Output assets/demo.gif

Set Width 800
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 22
Set FontFamily "monospace"
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Framerate 15

Hide
Env PS1 "$ "
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms

Type "typefully --help"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "typefully draft create --help"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
